### Register a new user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!",
  "firstName": "Test",
  "lastName": "User"
}

###

### Login to get the JWT Token
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

